        <p style="padding: 0 25px 0 25px;">
Yes, you can cancel or change your plan at any time for any reason with no penalty. There is no commitment and no contract that you are tied to.
</p>
<p style="padding: 0 25px 0 25px;">
For Plan changes, upgrades go into effect immediately. Plan downgrades go into effect at the beginning of your next billing cycle since bills are based on your past month&rsquo;s printing activity.
</p>
<p style="padding: 0 25px 0 25px;">
You can <a rel="noopener noreferrer" href="https://refreshezprintsubscription.brother-usa.com/Account/#/account/login" target="_blank" class="link link-external">cancel or change your plan on your Account Dashboard</a> 24/7. Simply go to Menu&gt;My Plans and Printers&gt;Click desired action. Before you cancel, please ensure you have non-Refresh subscription cartridge(s) ready to install. Your Refresh subscription cartridge(s) may stop working upon cancellation.
</p>
<p style="padding: 0 25px 0 25px;">
A Refresh Subscription Specialist can also assist you at <strong>(855) 996-0277</strong> weekdays 9 am to 9 pm ET.
</p>
